name: RE:custom
overview:
RE:custom is a blog about custom products and services, news and reviews about companies within the industry as well and trend information.

RE:custom is a new project by Blank Label Group, Inc. and is looking to increase awareness about the customization industry that will revolutionize the way we all consume products and services by allowing us to create, design and individualize everything we buy and the services we receive.

Blank Label Group, Inc.’s other companies include Blank Label, a customization website focusing on design-your-own dress shirts and Thread Tradition, another customization website focusing on fitted dress shirts.
